No. 85, No. 210,

Misc.

Misc.

Bascelio v. Mayo, State Prison Custodian; and Barber v. Bannan, Warden, et al.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus and for other relief denied. Treating the papers submitted as petitions for writs of certiorari, certiorari is ■ denied.
